---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="Write for Us" description="Contribute SaaS statistics articles to SaaSStatsHub.">
  <article class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto px-6 py-12 article-body">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Write for Us</h1>
    <p>SaaSStatsHub publishes data-rich SaaS statistics articles. If you're a researcher, analyst, or founder with original numbers to share, we'd love to hear from you.</p>

    <h2 id="what-we-publish">What We Publish</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Statistics roundups (30+ data points per article).</li>
      <li>Original research with disclosed methodology.</li>
      <li>Market analysis backed by primary sources.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 id="what-we-dont">What We Don't Publish</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Generic "top 10 SaaS tools" listicles.</li>
      <li>Pieces without verifiable sources.</li>
      <li>Pure product promotion or thinly-disguised ads.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 id="guidelines">Guidelines</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>1,500鈥?,000 words.</li>
      <li>Each statistic links to a primary source.</li>
      <li>Original data preferred; if you survey or scrape, share methodology.</li>
      <li>One DR60+ contextual link to your site allowed.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 id="how-to-pitch">How to Pitch</h2>
    <p>Email a 3-sentence pitch + outline + data sources to <a href="mailto:sangaypopo@gmail.com">sangaypopo@gmail.com</a>. We respond within a week. If accepted, drafts are due within 14 days.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
